      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Many humans thrive in racially diverse metropolitan areas, and some individuals are adopted by members of a different species. Humans with this species trait acquire a deep understanding of their adopted culture and gain a +2 species bonus to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.LeZmnFwnlB89ovBB]{Culture} checks to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.VWJLbwCeu7DsunHk]{Recall Knowledge} about non-humans and to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.aayAhTaRzitONs5U]{Disguise} checks to appear as a humanoid of another race.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces skilled.</strong></p>"
